0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:56:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89f0351803919bd519242b27c76d27ca326fc140","tid":2030113,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:20:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b91272a278ba1be86fb6f0fb357699dc6cfa0fce","tid":2030113,"uid":105090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"165cd39a9b58fbbbf0c0fb0c3b8a4eac67cb9db7","tid":2030113,"uid":131842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:33:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n我係 <a href=\"http://HKmap.live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHKmap.live&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=388eb8c8\" target=\"_blank\">HKmap.live</a> 既開發者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1438115/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1438115/page/1</a><br />\n見大家因為國安法開始搵VPN就黎開個Post講下<br />\n<br />\n想支持youtuber又想支持hkmap點好?<br />\n買PIA, 再將慳左既錢課金！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CdYC21e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCdYC21e.jpg&h=8513e102&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用VPN避免政府監察上網紀錄<br />\n一年 39.95 美金, 性價比最高<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkmap.live/pia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2Fpia&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=78c7f5fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/pia</a><br />\n^^^^^用呢條link^^^^^<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">已經係另一度買左3年又覺得唔岩用？其實一個月內可以申請退錢架</span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>有關PIA及其他VPN既見解</ins><br />\nPIA保障用家私隱係有court case&quot;證實&quot;<br />\n當然唔係話咁就100%可信，但唔會比大部分VPN差<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.technadu.com/private-internet-access-wins-against-fbi/30987/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.technadu.com%2Fprivate-internet-access-wins-against-fbi%2F30987%2F&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=fbc3e233\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.technadu.com/private-internet-access-wins-against-fbi/30987/</a><br />\n&quot;According to the evidence submitted in a local hacking case in San Jose, VPN PIA has a strict &lsquo;no-logging&rsquo; policy.<br />\nThis is the second time PIA had to prove their mettle in a federal court, and this is their second consecutive win.<br />\nVPNs, including PIA, evidently do not store the logs of users&rsquo; internet activities.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n用任何VPN都有可能被供應商出賣，而絕大部份主流供應商都有各種問題，另一方面又唔想大家集中某細供應商（上 HKmap 而有用 VPN 基本上都係最大果幾間），原因係如果一個供應商大部分用家都係一類人，咁你連 VPN 果下已經可以將你歸類，唔洗供應商出賣你，淨係睇你連接既 IP 已經夠做。<br />\n<br />\nKape 係收購左 PIA, 但除此之外 PIA 一直都紀錄良好。原 PIA 團隊都講左會繼續 0-log，講到尾如果你唔信原團隊，其實有無收購都唔應該用。Kape 2017 都買左 CyberGhost，而暫時都未聽過佢地有交log比執法機關政府等第三方。當年 Kape 係整 AdWare, 但依家 PIA clients 已經 open source，至少 client side 相對安全（and you can always use openvpn profile anyway）<a href=\"https://github.com/pia-foss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fpia-foss&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=e23ccaf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/pia-foss</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你係一般用家，我覺得任何一個主流 VPN 都足夠，睇價錢決定就得，可以既話就用crypto/giftcard比錢減少痕跡。如果你係要做敏感野，請用 Tor (Tor browser / Brave Tor mode) ，先係一個 trustless 既解決方案。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>以下係個人見解, 無VPN咩都最好</ins><br />\n自架: 容易設定錯誤及有IP聯繫<br />\nNord: 曾被入侵 用極多錢做marketing<br />\nExpress: 唯一中國用到既大VPN<br />\nWrap: 無法隱藏真 IP<br />\nSurfShark: 團隊及股東均匿名<br />\nProtonVPN: 相對安全但貴 免費版慢<br />\nHKGETV: 一個淨係得香港人既VPN未必理想<br />\n<br />\n轉埋更重視私隱既瀏覽器<br />\n<a href=\"https://brave.com/hkm851\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbrave.com%2Fhkm851&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=6bd9a0c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://brave.com/hkm851</a><br />\n<br />\n小貼士<br />\n1) 唔好用香港Server, 可選日本台灣等<br />\n2) 不時轉換Server <br />\n3) 避免用VPN登入政府/銀行等知道你真實身份既網站<br />\n4) 開 Kill switch (App設定) 避免 VPN 斷線導致 IP 洩漏<br />\n5) 唔好諗住有VPN就做乜都得<br />\n<br />\nP.S. <br />\n買咩VPN都好, 唔好咁傻豬直接走上人地個網買<br />\n盡量用HKmap或者其他Youtuber提供既Link/Code<br />\n所有不明來歷既code最後邊個食左d錢就自己諗啦<br />\n<br />\n請繼續支持持續運作近一年既HKmap<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkmap.live/pia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2Fpia&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=78c7f5fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/pia</a><br />\n<br />\n記得幫手報料呀 <a href=\"https://hkmap.live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=937c064d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T16:42:49.000Z","msg":"巴打，我換左新電話再拿唔到password，可以點做🙏"}]}